<P>
   Here are today's top news stories from The New York Times News
Service for AMs of Saturday, Dec. 11:
</P>
<P>
   &UR; INTERNATIONAL &LR;  (Moving in ``i'' news file.)
</P>
<P>
   EU-TURKEY (Helsinki, Finland) _ The European Union opened its
doors to Turkey's long-sought candidacy for membership Friday, but
placed many conditions. By Warren Hoge.
</P>
<P>
   EU-TURKET-REACT (Istanbul, Turkey) _ Reaction to the news in
Turkey. By Stephen Kinzer.
