<P>
   JERRYS-DELI _ Jerry's Famous Deli Inc. will consolidate its
shares in a 1-for-3 reverse split and petition Nasdaq to move its
listing to the SmallCap market in an attempt to avoid being dumped
in Nasdaq's OTC listing, the company's board announced Friday.
Directors of the Studio City-based restaurant chain said they still
hope to convince Nasdaq to keep Jerry's on the national listing. By
Chris Sieroty. (Will move on the ``f'' financial wire.)
